<p>We will use the information we receive only for the purposes that are described in this Privacy Policy. Please note that we do not control and is not responsible for other uses of your Personal Information by your third-party social media provider. Therefore, we recommend that you review their privacy policy to understand how they collect, use and share your Personal Information and how you can set your privacy preferences on their site.</p>
